# Hermes Agent 1-Click notes
#
# Hermes user:  hermes
# Hermes home:  /home/hermes/.hermes
# Workspace:    /home/hermes/workspace
#
# Configure providers with:
#   sudo -u hermes -H /home/hermes/.local/bin/hermes setup
# or:
#   hermes setup
#
# Provider keys are stored in /home/hermes/.hermes/.env by Hermes itself.
